{"tid":930237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為三父女 三個人 三個姓","createTime":"2018-12-06T07:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T10:41:08.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0c41a47962710d3e04aeda4943aa905ae60dad","tid":930237,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"1：任正非個大女，點解姓孟？有傳任正非受恩於妻子孟軍一家，所以入贅孟家。至於任正非就曾解釋過，喺外父身上學到唔少嘢，所以畀個女跟公公姓。至於孟晚舟本人曾講過，名係佢16歲時自己改，跟母親姓。至於任正非同孟軍都生個咗個仔，都係跟阿媽姓，叫孟平。<br />\n<br />\n2：至於後生遙遙嘅任正非細女其實係姓姚，叫Annebel Yao，都係跟阿媽姓，即係任正非第二任妻子姚凌。本來冇人知有呢個女，直至佢應邀出席巴黎名媛舞會Le Bal des D&eacute;butantes，仲高調接受專訪，先有人知佢嘅存在。哈佛學生，讀計算機科學，同何猷君、何超欣係Friend，今次可以出席上個月嘅舞會，都係何超欣推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181206/large/1544071064_b435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181206%2Flarge%2F1544071064_b435.jpg&h=aa17ce0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181206/58998085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F58998085&d=OnQhE1jfOhsITLw1mWoZi3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=deed6f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F58998085&h=391e17b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181206/58998085</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aae24925158539494e55d931aed856d07237234","tid":930237,"uid":41821,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"姓黨咪唔洗煩囉"},{"pid":"0e88b3355d2049e4087537d9c55ee5c0a59d53b5","tid":930237,"uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-